# Birthday Module ‚Äî Redesign Plan (Updated)

## Goal

Rebuild the Birthday module with 3 pages:

1. **Birthday List** ‚Äî All users from `userDetail` with DOB, with canva/template status linked inline (approve/reject/add)
2. **Dashboard** ‚Äî Today / Tomorrow / Yesterday / Day‚Äëbefore‚Äëyesterday birthdays, filtered to only **approved** canva entries + unsent messages
3. **Add Canva** ‚Äî Create new birthday creative (defaults to `pending`)

> [!NOTE]
> The previous "All Users Birthday List" and "Canva Status List" are now **merged into one page** (`/admin/birthday/list`). This page reads from `userDetail` and cross-references `birthdayCanva` to show canva status inline per user.

